    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Comedy Misfits: Life on the Road (19+)";
  schema:description """
	What do you get when three misfits who barely know each other pile into one van across Canada on a comedy tour? Plenty of jokes — and the real stories they'd never tell on stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Encore Tickets $26.50</span> - Throw a little extra love to a Fringe Artist. - It's like tipping your favorite server, but with way more glitter and a lot less drama! Our Fringe Artist wallets thank you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)
""";
