  schema:name "Cric! Crac! Crone Bones Singing (18+)";
  schema:description """
	<h2>with Storyteller Margaret Murphy</h2><span><br/></span>Rise Up Beloved Crones, Women of the Wild! Welcome Wise-Hearted all! Join this Celebration of Magical Mischief~  Stories and Rememberings of our Heart Wisdom. We are the Conspiracy of Crones! Cric! Crac!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Encore Tickets $26.50</span> - Throw a little extra love to a Fringe Artist. - It's like tipping your favorite server, but with way more glitter and a lot less drama! Our Fringe Artist wallets thank you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)
""";
