	<span class=\"BoldText\">Ages 19+</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A lecture-performance built like a forensic thriller: how five minutes of nudity in my solo show ended up on adult forums without my consent, and the surreal encounters with the men who lurk there.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Encore Tickets $26.50</span> - Throw a little extra love to a Fringe Artist. - It's like tipping your favorite server, but with way more glitter and a lot less drama! Our Fringe Artist wallets thank you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)
""";
