  schema:name "Fringe Festival 5 Show Pass";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Available through to August 16th, 2026</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Purchase</span> a 5-Show Pass, here's how it works:<span><br/></span>1. Purchase a pass by clicking the <span class=\"BoldText\">BUY PASS</span> button<span><br/></span>2. Redeem pass for up to 5 tickets<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Redeem</span> a 5-Show Pass, here's how it works:<span><br/></span>You can decide at time of purchasing the pass to add up to 5 tickets to your cart<span><br/></span>or<span><br/></span>You can <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.porttheatre.com/login/\">Login</a> to the same user account at a later date to redeem the pass any time prior to August 17th<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you prefer, you can contact The Port Theatre Ticket Centre at <span class=\"BoldText\">250-754-8550</span> and a Ticket Clerk can help you redeem your 5-Show Pass. They can also provide you with information regarding accessible seating.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All passes are sold through the Port Theatre Ticket Centre, online & by phone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)
""";
