<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/80401ARTSPVHDDBJHRKBQKPHQDNLHVQMC> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Great Canadian Road Trip";
  schema:description """
	Great Canadian road trip tour  brings together three of Canada’s most celebrated country music icons for an unforgettable evening of stories, songs, and shared memories. Featuring legendary performers Doc Walker, Jason McCoy, and Michelle Wight, the tour offers audiences a rare and intimate experience that goes beyond music. Fans will hear the personal stories and inspirations behind beloved hits while enjoying stunning visuals and heartfelt performances that celebrate Canada’s rich country music legacy.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Since forming in 1994, Doc Walker has become one of Canada’s most awarded country acts, earning a Juno award, 14 CCMA awards and countless chart topping singles and videos. Joining them is two time CCMA male vocalist, Hall of Famer, and reigning CCMA artist and Personality of the year Jason McCoy, whose career spans more than 34 years as both solo artist and front man of the Road Hammers. Also taking the stage is Michelle Wright one of  Canada’s most internationally recognized country stars and a Canadian country Music Hall Fame inductee.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Together, these celebrated artists create an evening filled with nostalgia, connection, laughter, and the timeless soundtrack of Canadian country music.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-10-25T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/files/f0123d37-41cd-48b7-885e-f8ef147be77a.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/theporttheatre/location/407AGBMNMGJMSNPVKJMSNVLRPHJBTDPHT>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/theporttheatre/organization/gee-dan-productions>;
  schema:offers _:57e8ee661ad740a08e5ad0ea20bc4b344993;
  schema:keywords "Music";
  schema:duration "PT120M";
  schema:endDate "2026-10-25T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

