<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/68201ATPHPGBHMDNSHHSTPHBMQBRQBLST> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "POPS: The Music of James Bond ";
  schema:description """
	GUEST CONDUCTOR: Scott MacInnes<span><br/></span>GUEST ARTIST: Jeans ‘n Classics Band<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From smoky ballads to explosive orchestral moments, danger has never sounded this good. This Bond-inspired concert features unforgettable themes like For Your Eyes<span><br/></span>Only, Skyfall, and Live and Let Die, inviting you into a world of spies, secrets, and music that’s unmistakably... shaken, not stirred.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Slip into your favourite Bond-inspired look, walk the red carpet, and snap some glam shots.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Read more about the Vancouver Island Symphony, Guest Artists and the music at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vancouverislandsymphony.com\"> www.vancouverislandsymphony.com</a> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Driven by Passion. United in Sound</span><span><br/></span>Stay updated on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanislesymphony\"> Facebook</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vancouverislandsymphony/\"> Instagram</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Multi show discounts available</span>; simply add the 3 POPS shows to your shopping cart to see your savings!</h2>
""";
