<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/86004AHPSPTVSVKQPKTBDJMMJGCSQVGNM> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "PTS Tea";
  schema:description """
	After her murdered daughter returns as a spirit narrator, a Métis Cree mother and her daughters navigate intergenerational trauma, PTSD, and systemic failure. Through dark humour, culture, and fierce love, they resist inherited cycles of domestic violence—fighting for what healing is possible.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Encore Tickets $26.50</span> - Throw a little extra love to a Fringe Artist. - It's like tipping your favorite server, but with way more glitter and a lot less drama! Our Fringe Artist wallets thank you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-08-12T18:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
