<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/61001AVKKRKGPQTDBMRDKCBQMCGNRHLKS> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sixx Paxx - 19+ Only";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">WHEN FANTASIES COME TRUE</span>  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Close your eyes and imagine your wildest night out—then watch it come to life. The SIXX PAXX DREAMS TOUR arrives in 2026/27, taking the internationally acclaimed sensation to the biggest stages they’ve ever played.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This all-new production turns up the heat with more seduction, more passion, and more unforgettable moments—featuring electrifying choreography, live vocals, and a high-impact show that begins like a dream and stays with you long after the final bow.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Perfect for a girls’ night out, birthday celebration, or bachelorette party, SIXX PAXX delivers an interactive, high-energy experience where fantasy meets world-class performance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This is a 19+ Event</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sixxpaxx.com\"> Website</a> / <span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\" https://www.instagram.com/thesixxpaxx/ \"> INSTA</a> / <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sixxpaxxde\"> FB</a> / <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.forrestjonesentertainment.com\"> Promoter</a>  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
