<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/81801ATHJBGSKNNNRKKRCMBNCKDNKRPGD> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "SIZZLE: Three to Tango";
  schema:description """
	By popular demand, the Marko Paolo Trio returns with their irresistible mix of charm and virtuosity. You’ll be swept up in the Trio’s trademark flair as they transform familiar favourites into something fresh and unforgettable — guiding you through an eclectic blend of classical masterworks, fiery tangos, folky classics, and there might even be a sing along. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>MUSICIANS<span><br/></span>Mark Beaty, Bass; Paolo Bortolussi, Flute; Calvin Dyck, Violin & Accordion<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>PROGRAMME*<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>HAYDN:  London Trios<span><br/></span>SHOSTAKOVICH:  Waltz #2 <span><br/></span>IBERT: ENtr’Acte<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>CONSTANTINI: Valse des Adieux<span><br/></span>GARDEL: Por Una Cabeza<span><br/></span>PIAZZOLLA: Four Seasons of Buenos Aires<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>MACGILLVRAY: Song for the Mira<span><br/></span>STAN ROGERS: Jeannie C<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*programming subject to change<span><br/></span>
""";
