<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/74401AGBSSPNCNSTSGRQKGQGNLKKTDHTV> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Take It To The Limit ";
  schema:description """
	Eagles fans! Get ready for an unforgettable live concert experience with \"Take It to The Limit\", celebrating the songs, stories and legacy of the Eagles!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Returning to the Port Theatre in Nanaimo for one night on November 2nd!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Experience the magic as \"Take It To The Limit\" brings to life your favorite Eagles hits, including classics like Hotel California, Heartache Tonight, Peaceful Easy Feeling, Take It To The Limit, Take It Easy, Lyin' Eyes, Desperado, Long Run, New Kid In Town, Tequila Sunrise, Best Of My Love, I Can't Tell You Why, Witchy Woman and many more! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With rave reviews from coast to coast, this show promises to be a fully immersive experience, capturing the essence and energy of an authentic Eagles concert. Even NHL Hall of Famer Glenn Anderson is a fan! “I saw Take It To The Limit tonight and they were fantastic! I highly recommend them. Good energy. Good people and lots of fun. Make sure you make it to the show – you have a good time coming.”<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>📣Here’s what fans are saying 🫶<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Saw them in Sacramento last December. If you closed your eyes you would swear you were listening to the Eagles. They are a fantastic band.” -  John Nelson – Sacramento, CA<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"These guys are the real deal. I Enjoyed their Eagles music at the Fox Theatre in Tucson last year.. an epic concert!”-  Janet Welty – Tucson, AZ<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“One of the best I’ve seen! If anyone has the chance to see these guys perform, it’s well worth going. Everything from sound, stage, lighting & vocals were perfect. A great show!“  - Angie Tatarniuk – Vancouver, BC<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Hi! Thank you for a wonderful evening tonight. My husband and I thoroughly enjoyed your talents. Someone behind me said “if you close your eyes, you would think it was The Eagles.” – Diana Owens - Wenatchee, WA<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Saw them in Olympia, WA, Oct. '25. Tribute band sounded as great as original Eagles. Wonderful evening. The band made you feel so welcome and happy to entertain you. Young and old, go see.” - Becky Heffernan - Olympia, WA<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Just saw this group last night in Yakima Washington. Absolutely the best concert I've ever heard. Absolutely phenomenal! Would recommend to everyone! You don't want to miss them.” - Lora Dykes - Yakima Washington. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>📣 Press Reviews: 🫶<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Amazing Eagle’s Tribute! The band did not disappoint with a note-for-note tribute to the American rock icons. My guests were blown away! Congrats for the amazing success!“   – Tom Zillich, Entertainment Reporter - Surrey Now-Leader<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“This group of master musicians are building a legion of fans internationally and racking up spectacular reviews as they continue to hold their position as the definitive Eagles tribute group.” – Roger W Morgan, The Legend 105.9 FM - Coos Bay, OR<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss this extraordinary celebration of the Eagles’ legendary music. Gather your friends and family for an evening of timeless hits and unforgettable memories!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>More info at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://EaglesTributeShow.com\">EaglesTributeShow.com</a><span><br/></span>or Follow the group on Facebook, Instagram & TikTok @EaglesTributeShow<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
