    schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Beastly Thing";
  schema:description """
	Tormented by the monster living under her bed, May grapples with self worth, loneliness, and binging to the extreme. As it feeds on May’s growing shame, she begins to lose herself slowly but surely to The Beastly Thing.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Encore Tickets $26.50</span> - Throw a little extra love to a Fringe Artist. - It's like tipping your favorite server, but with way more glitter and a lot less drama! Our Fringe Artist wallets thank you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)
""";
