<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/67201AVCRKQDBSGLQHRCLJQTBDLCTLNNQ> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Winter Glow";
  schema:description """
	PRE-CONCERT TALK 6:30PM   CONCERT 7:30PM  <span><br/></span>GUEST CONDUCTOR: Dina Gilbert<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From Caroline Shaw’s playful Entr’acte to Shostakovich’s Chamber Symphony, this concert highlights an expressive range of music written for string orchestra, offering moments of reflection amidst stark intensity, culminating in warmth and contentment. A perfect programme for a winter night.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Programme:<span><br/></span>SHAW: Entr’acte<span><br/></span>SHOSTAKOVICH: Chamber Symphony in C minor, Op. 110a<span><br/></span>BARBER: Adagio for Strings<span><br/></span>TCHAIKOVSKY: Serenade for Strings, Op. 48<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Read more about the Vancouver Island Symphony, Guest Artists and the music at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vancouverislandsymphony.com\"> www.vancouverislandsymphony.com</a> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Driven by Passion. United in Sound</span><span><br/></span>Stay updated on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanislesymphony\"> Facebook</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vancouverislandsymphony/\"> Instagram</a><span><br/></span>
""";
