    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Woman in White vs the KGB (Outdoor Stage)";
  schema:description """
	When the Woman in White arrives in Marc’s weekend writing course followed by Lovecraft, a diabolical KGB operative, heart stopping spy thriller becomes the genre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Encore Tickets $26.50</span> - Throw a little extra love to a Fringe Artist. - It's like tipping your favorite server, but with way more glitter and a lot less drama! Our Fringe Artist wallets thank you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All patrons are required to purchase a <span class=\"BoldText\">$5.00 FRINGE FESTIVAL BUTTON</span> to see any shows. Proceeds support the operating costs of the Nanaimo Fringe Festival. (If you lose or forget your button you will need to purchase another)<span><br/></span>
""";
