 piece of theatre written from a perspective and voice we need to hear.”</span> ~ <span class=\"BoldText\">Winnipeg Free Press</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“Not only is the play a fun and clever look at history, but by weaving in modern slang and references, Koncan highlights how many Indigenous issues from our past are still relevant today”</span> ~ <span class=\"BoldText\">CBC News</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">CONTENT WARNING</span><span><br/></span>This event contains the following: swearing, discriminatory themes, stage gunfire and war sounds, disturbing content, reference to hanging and execution<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Recommended Age: 13+<span><br/></span>
""";
